class animLayer(object):
    '''The TdnAnimLayer node is used to provide fine grain control over animations.  Animations
 are built up using a sequence of animation layers to create the final output.
 Animation layers are built within this node where each layer contains attributes that
 are keyed.  This node manages the input of this information and passes the data to pairBlend
 nodes for mixing the layers together. The control of the blending between layers is done
 by setting weights. Child layers can also have child layers which adds to the
 flexibility of animation setup.
