class keyingGroup(object):
    '''The keyingGroup node is a special type of set. It is used to gather
  together animatable attributes. These attributes can then be animated
        and edited in unison.
KeyingGroup sets may only contain animatable attributes and other
  keying groups.
Objects within keying groups can be designated activator objects. When a
  key is set on an activator object, it triggers keyframing of the other
  objects within the keyingGroup.
Maya also maintains a global keyingGroup filter preference which can be used
