        |  0    0    1    0 |          |  0    0    1    0 |
        | rpx  rpy  rpz   1 |          | rptx rpty rptz  1 |
RA = AX * AY * AZ
AX = |  1    0    0    0 |     AY = |  cy   0   -sy   0 |
        |  0    cx   sx   0 |          |  0    1    0    0 |
        |  0   -sx   cx   0 |          |  sy   0    cy   0 |
        |  0    0    0    1 |          |  0    0    0    1 |
AZ = |  cz   sz   0    0 |     sx = sin(rax), cx = cos(rax)
        | -sz   cz   0    0 |     sy = sin(ray), cx = cos(ray)
        |  0    0    1    0 |     sz = sin(raz), cz = cos(raz)
